chunks.plain_content:
File your gambling tax return
Log in to your HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) online account and file your returns for General Betting Duty, Pool Betting Duty or Remote Gaming Duty.

chunks.html_content: Online services may be slow during busy times. Check if there are any problems with this service.
chunks.plain_content:
File your gambling tax return
Online services may be slow during busy times. Check if there are any problems with this service.

chunks.html_content:
Youll need:

  • an HMRC online account
  • a Government Gateway user ID and password - if you do not have a user ID, you can create one when you use the service

Check if you need to register and pay General Betting Duty, Pool Betting Duty or Remote Gaming Duty.
chunks.plain_content:
File your gambling tax return
Youll need:

  an HMRC online account
  a Government Gateway user ID and password - if you do not have a user ID, you can create one when you use the service

Check if you need to register and pay General Betting Duty, Pool Betting Duty or Remote Gaming Duty.

chunks.html_content: You must submit your returns online if you hold a remote operating licence from the Gambling Commission.
chunks.plain_content:
File your gambling tax return
You must submit your returns online if you hold a remote operating licence from the Gambling Commission.

chunks.html_content: You can continue to file paper returns if you do not hold a remote operating licence. HMRC will send you a paper return for each accounting period.
chunks.plain_content:
File your gambling tax return
You can continue to file paper returns if you do not hold a remote operating licence. HMRC will send you a paper return for each accounting period.
